{"tid":1561593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【願榮光歸香港】絕對可以做國歌","createTime":"2019-09-11T15:58:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T16:07:57.000Z","uid":277916,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"be9078a604534a1ea998232f1da137151ee949de","tid":1561593,"uid":277916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:58:20.000Z","msg":"所謂國家，就係一群人嘅集體身分認同<br />\n要建構呢個身分認同，係建基於呢個族群嘅集體回憶同文化<br />\n香港人一直都有獨特嘅文化<br />\n在此唔多講<br />\n但集體回憶，好多時就同佢哋共同經歷嘅苦難同喜悅有關<br />\n而最重要嘅記憶通常都係佢哋嘅建國過程<br />\n唔少國家都係經歷戰火先得到族群嘅自由，得以浴火重生<br />\n好似美國，佢哋嘅國歌就係獨立戰爭嘅軍歌<br />\n（支共就收皮啦，佢哋係騎劫民國打抗日嘅功勞喳）<br />\n有人話軍歌唔應該做國歌，其實呢個係無必然嘅邏輯關係<br />\n軍歌點解唔可以做國歌，就算唔係戰爭時候<br />\n只要呢首歌係敘述我哋嘅立國過程同立國精神<br />\n就足以成為一首國歌<br />\n我哋作國歌就係想日後嘅下一代可以傳承我哋嘅革命精神，捍衛我哋嘅革命成果<br />\n由佢哋繼續述說「香港人」嘅故事<br />\n<br />\n或者歌詞係有啲繞口同埋沙石<br />\n可以少改<br />\n不過唔好忘記有約定俗成<br />\n呢首歌已經刻入越嚟越多香港人嘅心裡<br />\n改唔改，已經無所謂了"},{"pid":"3832c51bb0f9d94d75473135efbd3b3da94182be","tid":1561593,"uid":5682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:58:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 遮打見！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qftu6C0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqftu6C0.jpg&h=23ce3992&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<di