=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"260de8bd66796f114b8dafbb2618e7bf5fa74c7c","tid":1561593,"uid":38540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:00:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港急需一首歌去團結民族！<br />\n呢首唔係最完美但我可以肯定講係最合時！！！</span>"},{"pid":"9ff9eb4439e44c77249c38ae35c0fff20463d2ba","tid":1561593,"uid":277916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"260de8bd66796f114b8dafbb2618e7bf5fa74c7c","tid":1561593,"uid":38540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:00:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港急需一首歌去團結民族！<br />\n呢首唔係最完美但我可以肯定講係最合時！！！</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:02:33.000Z","msg":"我覺得暫時仲未諗到將來可以作到一首比佢更好<br />\n但係只要係有份參與呢場運動嘅人<br />\n都會認同佢係最代表到呢場運動同香港人<br />\n所以一旦我哋有機會成功<br />\n佢都好大機會會成為國歌"},{"pid":"76f0515f45223afcc09bce8a30df3887a36a9300","tid":1561593,"uid":277916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:04:21.000Z","msg":"十連推開始<br />\n1/10"},{"pid":"38a906f613e5bf2f5ecd0ea5fc336e5fa299fd8f","tid":1561593,"uid":277916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:04:33.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"3c8bde40cbb521139f50cd25cd64509e083d8de2","tid":1561593,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:04:38.000Z","msg":"唱完要推返915 300萬人遊行 同929 101 全球反共日呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f1c3